      <mri:abstract>
        <gco:CharacterString>Urban Atlas Land Cover/Land Use 2018 provides reliable, inter-comparable, high-resolution land use and land cover data for 764 Functional Urban Areas (FUA) with more than 50,000 inhabitants for the 2018 reference year in EEA38 countries (EU, EFTA, Western Balkans countries, as well as Türkiye) and the United Kingdom.</gco:CharacterString>
